name: IBANCheckDigit_calculateTest
description: Unit tests for the IBANCheckDigit class, focusing on the calculate and isValid methods.

test_cases.name: testCalculateValidCode
test_cases.description: Tests the calculate method with a valid IBAN code.

test_cases.name: testCalculateInvalidCodeLength
test_cases.description: Tests the calculate method with an invalid IBAN code length, expecting a CheckDigitException.

test_cases.name: testCalculateNullCode
test_cases.description: Tests the calculate method with a null IBAN code, expecting a CheckDigitException.

test_cases.name: testIsValidWithValidCode
test_cases.description: Tests the isValid method with a valid IBAN code.

test_cases.name: testIsValidWithInvalidCodeLength
test_cases.description: Tests the isValid method with an invalid IBAN code length.

test_cases.name: testIsValidWithNullCode
test_cases.description: Tests the isValid method with a null IBAN code.
